Subjetivo 
 # # ATENDIMENTO NEUROLOGIA AMBULATORIAL # # 
 > <PATIENT>Rafael</PATIENT/> <PATIENT>Freitas</PATIENT/>, <AGE>52</AGE/> anos, <PROFESSION>engenheiro</PROFESSION/> <PROFESSION>civil</PROFESSION/>, vindo de <CITY>Salvador</CITY/> 
